## Run tests

**unit tests**
```
pip install -e .[test]
pytest -xvs tests/unit
```

**integration tests**
```
pip install -e .[test]
docker-compose -f tests/integration/compose/docker-compose.yml up -d
IP_HOST=localhost pytest -xvs tests/integration
```


